text: (Pangandikane Allah), "Ahli - ahli Negara sadurunge wong - wong kafir mau iya padha nyuwun tandha yekti kaelokan. Bareng wis Ingsun paringi, isih tetep padha ora gelem percaya, wusana banjur padha Ingsun tumpes (rusak). Saiki menawa Ingsun paringi tandha yekti, wong - wong kafir mau apa iya banjur padha percaya
